 i te neke poruvi,

457
00:44:00,440 --> 00:44:01,060
 jel, ali dobro,

458
00:44:01,060 --> 00:44:02,200
 evo, sve za već je dobro.

459
00:44:02,200 --> 00:44:03,280
 Tako da svako,

460
00:44:03,280 --> 00:44:04,400
 znaju o svi poduzetni,

461
00:44:04,400 --> 00:44:05,540
 su se sigurno nekad našli

462
00:44:05,540 --> 00:44:07,240
 koji su nešto inovativno osmislili,

463
00:44:07,240 --> 00:44:08,220
 našli su se u toj fazi

464
00:44:08,220 --> 00:44:09,200
 da moraš petrpeti

465
00:44:09,200 --> 00:44:10,780
 ljusku ironiju i smijeh,

466
00:44:10,780 --> 00:44:12,700
 jel, i onda ustrajati u tome.

467
00:44:12,700 --> 00:44:14,660
 Onda znaš da si na dobrom putu.

468
00:44:14,660 --> 00:44:15,620
 Je, je, je.

469
00:44:15,620 --> 00:44:16,120
 A mislim,

470
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:18,500
 nekako znaš u srcu

471
00:44:18,500 --> 00:44:19,420
 kad imaš taj mir,

472
00:44:19,420 --> 00:44:21,240
 ali ja uvijek vjerujem

473
00:44:21,240 --> 00:44:23,460
 kad ti Bog daje neko poslanje

474
00:44:23,460 --> 00:44:24,300
 ili nešto da ti daje

475
00:44:24,300 --> 00:44:26,640
 dovoljno i snage

476
00:44:26,640 --> 00:44:29,200
 i da te ne slome te stvari.

477
00:44:29,200 --> 00:44:31,440
 Evo, tako da...

478
00:44:31,440 --> 00:44:32,040
 Odlično.

479
00:44:32,040 --> 00:44:34,020
 Evo, moramo završiti emisiju.

480
00:44:34,020 --> 00:44:36,260
 Ja ću završiti,

481
00:44:36,260 --> 00:44:37,400
 spomenula si egzamen

482
00:44:37,400 --> 00:44:38,500
 i svijetog Ignacija,

483
00:44:38,500 --> 00:44:39,400
 koliko je važan.

484
00:44:39,400 --> 00:44:40,640
 Meni isto

485
00:44:40,640 --> 00:44:44,000
 Ignacive vježbe su bile važne.

486
00:44:44,000 --> 00:44:45,980
 Da isto si,

487
00:44:45,980 --> 00:44:48,340
 shvatim neke stvari u svom životu,

488
00:44:48,340 --> 00:44:51,380
 pa jedna važna rečenca

489
00:44:51,380 --> 00:44:52,420
 koja stoji,

490
00:44:52,420 --> 00:44:53,120
 a to je

491
00:44:53,120 --> 00:44:54,200
 čovjek je stvoren

492
00:44:54,200 --> 00:44:56,420
 da gospodina Boga svoga hvali,

493
00:44:56,420 --> 00:44:57,680
 da ga štuje,

494
00:44:57,680 --> 00:44:58,620
 da mu služi

495
00:44:58,620 --> 00:45:00,800
 i da tako spasi dušu svoju.

496
00:45:01,440 --> 00:45:03,500
 A ostale stvari na zemlji

497
00:45:03,500 --> 00:45:05,440
 stvorene su radi čovjeka

498
00:45:05,440 --> 00:45:07,240
 da mu budu od pomoći

499
00:45:07,240 --> 00:45:08,500
 i da postigne svrhu

500
00:45:08,500 --> 00:45:10,200
 za koji je stvoren.

501
00:45:10,200 --> 00:45:12,500
 Evo.

502
00:45:12,500 --> 00:45:13,900
 Evo, to što se sad izrekla,

503
00:45:13,900 --> 00:45:15,180
 to nam je nekako je slogan

504
00:45:15,180 --> 00:45:15,780
 u našoj,

505
00:45:15,780 --> 00:45:17,820
 naveden u svim našim brošurama.

506
00:45:17,820 --> 00:45:19,380
 Evo, naziv sam

507
00:45:19,380 --> 00:45:20,140
 Praise,

508
00:45:20,140 --> 00:45:21,140
 došao od riječi

509
00:45:21,140 --> 00:45:22,400
 zapravo slaviti,

510
00:45:22,400 --> 00:45:24,520
 a baš je inspiriran

511
00:45:24,520 --> 00:45:25,840
 na čelom Svetog Ignacije,

512
00:45:25,840 --> 00:45:27,040
 tako da se pogodila u sredu

513
00:45:27,040 --> 00:45:27,840
 s ovim citatom

514
00:45:27,840 --> 00:45:29,360
 i za okruživanjem.

515
00:45:29,360 --> 00:45:30,940
 Praise the Lord.

516
00:45:31,440 --> 00:45:32,920
 Da, da, da, da.

517
00:45:32,920 --> 00:45:34,520
 Pre iz engleski naziv sad

518
00:45:34,520 --> 00:45:36,440
 neke stvari smo izmijenili,

519
00:45:36,440 --> 00:45:37,660
 počeo je baš zato da bi

520
00:45:37,660 --> 00:45:39,000
 do...

521
00:45:39,000 --> 00:45:40,260
 Jer sam ja došla iz

522
00:45:40,260 --> 00:45:41,860
 ono, života prije,

523
00:45:41,860 --> 00:45:42,380
 ajmo reći,

524
00:45:42,380 --> 00:45:43,400
 onda sam htjela da to

525
00:45:43,400 --> 00:45:44,680
 predo što većeg broja ljudi,

526
00:45:44,680 --> 00:45:46,280
 neovisno da li su vjernici ili ne.

527
00:45:46,280 --> 00:45:48,080
 Evo, tako da.

528
00:45:48,260 --> 00:45:50,800
 Pa je, Bog je stvorio svih nas

529
00:45:50,800 --> 00:45:52,660
 i ubiti nam je dao zadaću,

530
00:45:52,660 --> 00:45:54,520
 evo, da svakome širimo

531
00:45:54,520 --> 00:45:57,680
 njegovu radosno vijest,

532
00:45:57,680 --> 00:45:59,280
 a sad svako ima slobodu

533
00:45:59,280 --> 00:46:00,000
 da odabere

534
00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:01,480
 da li će on tu

535
00:46:01,480 --> 00:46:03,540
 radosno vijest prihvatiti ili ne.

536
00:46:03,540 --> 00:46:04,740
 Tako je.

537
00:46:05,140 --> 00:46:07,580
 Vesna, evo, ako nešto želiš još

538
00:46:07,580 --> 00:46:10,280
 ili pozdraviti naše slušatelje

539
00:46:10,280 --> 00:46:12,260
 i gledatelje.

540
00:46:12,260 --> 00:46:13,860
 Pa evo, samo bih htjela evo crca

541
00:46:13,860 --> 00:46:14,900
 pozdraviti sve

542
00:46:14,900 --> 00:46:16,020
 i evo nam se da vam je bilo

543
00:46:16,020 --> 00:46:17,380
 na blagoslov i plodonosno

544
00:46:17,380 --> 00:46:18,960
 ako je bilo kojima je ovo koristilo

545
00:46:18,960 --> 00:46:19,920
 makar jednoj osobi

546
00:46:19,920 --> 00:46:20,800
 evo, nama je drago

547
00:46:20,800 --> 00:46:21,900
 da smo se ovdje našli

548
00:46:21,900 --> 00:46:24,360
 i da smo malo popričali s vama.

549
00:46:24,360 --> 00:46:25,480
 Eto, hvala svima

550
00:46:25,480 --> 00:46:26,740
 i vidimo se drugi put.

551
00:46:26,740 --> 00:46:27,860
 Vidimo se.

552
00:46:27,860 --> 00:46:31,880
 Evo, moje ime je Katarina Bukša

553
00:46:31,880 --> 00:46:33,460
 ja sam urednica i voditeljica

554
00:46:33,460 --> 00:46:36,140
 emisije Franjena ekonomija.

555
00:46:36,140 --> 00:46:38,680
 Tehnički urednik je danas bio

556
00:46:38,680 --> 00:46:40,500
 Marijan Agričić.

557
00:46:40,500 --> 00:46:41,840
 Hvala nisu si Marija.

558
00:47:03,460 --> 00:47:12,120
 Tvoja slava

559
00:47:12,120 --> 00:47:15,060
 oh

